13/02/2011
PODGORICA, Montenegro -- Interior and Public Administration Minister Ivan Brajovic announced on Friday (February 11th) that the country will start issuing citizenship declarations and various other birth certification documents with unlimited term of validity. In an interview with the Pobjeda daily, Brajovic said measure aims to rationalise administrative procedures. (Pobjeda, Kurir, Blic - 11/02/11)
